title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Monetized Friendship
description:
We had no choice but to bring back that old TF feeling for our best friends behind the paywall as there was just way too much crucial information to unpack this week, such as like for example: what we wore to James’ tasteful and safe 34th birthday party, when will we realistically record in person again, mental health checks, lifestyle changes, losing money, haircuts, arguing about Kanye West running for president and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
